  <summary date="2019-01-08T15:03:24Z" status="Introduced in House">Do Not Track Kids Act of 2018

This bill addresses the collection and publication of children's personal and geolocation information by operators of websites, online services or applications, or mobile applications directed to children or minors.

It also prohibits use of any such information to target marketing to children.</summary>
